        <h1>About RENDEZVOUS Badminton Academy</h1>
        <p>
          RENDEZVOUS Badminton Academy is dedicated to nurturing young badminton enthusiasts into world-class players.
          Established in 2010, we provide professional coaching, rigorous training programs, and state-of-the-art facilities to players of all levels.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is to blend <strong>discipline</strong>, <strong>technique</strong>, and <strong>passion</strong> to develop champions both on and off the court.
          Our experienced coaching staff are committed to every student's success, helping players build physical fitness, tactical knowledge, and mental toughness.
        </p>
        <p>
          Join RBA to become part of a supportive and competitive community that values personal growth and athletic excellence.
        </p>
